				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">shadowzero313 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">This is kinda OT, but if I have the tip polarity set right, can I use a plain 9VDC adapter inplace of the original 9VAC the NES used?</div>
<br />
<br />Since the NES takes 9VAC, I believe you can give it DC in <em>either</em> polarity and it'll work fine (since it'll just run it through a rectifier anyways).</div>

					
